## make manifest， 样品地址构建，对于双端序列对应三列，第一列史sampleid，其余两列史正链与反链路径
```
python /home/jhtang/mytest/code/process_16S/manifest_paired.py -s .R -m .R \
-d /home/LDlab/wangying/DXX/fourth_batch_16S_20200527/fourth_batch_2

usage: manifest_paired.py [-h] [-s SEPERATOR] [-m METASEPERATOR] [-d DATA]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s SEPERATOR, --seperator SEPERATOR
                        the seperator for seperate the file name,default is .R
                        for L.326.R1.fq.gz
  -m METASEPERATOR, --metaSeperator METASEPERATOR
                        the seperator for seperate the file name,default is
                        .fastq.gz for A75.fastq.gz
  -d DATA, --data DATA  the path of the data folder

```

### for paired end , 将下列代码整合到一个目录，命名为run_qiime.sh, 然后通过 bash run_qiime.sh 运行


